    dc:description "FIGURES 54–59. Metriocnemus fuscipes-type: 54—head capsule. Orthocladius (Orthocladius) dentifer-type: 55—head capsule. Orthocladius (Mesorthocladius) frigidus: 56—head capsule (arrow indicates seta submenti). Orthocladius (Euorthocladius): 57—head capsule. Parametriocnemus/Paraphaenocladius: 58 (arrow indicates seta submenti). Parorthocladius: 59—head capsule." ;
